Feature: Tracking
 
    Scenario: Search for all world covid statistics
     Given the url "http://localhost:8080/"
     When the customer want's to check today world data
     And he/she clicks in "All Countries" side bar button
     Then he/she should see the following message "Today's World Data"

    Scenario: See Croatia statistics
     Given the url "http://localhost:8080/countrydata"
     When the customer searches for 'Portugal'
     Then Portugal statistics are presented in a table

    Scenario: User searches for a nonexistent country
     Given the url "http://localhost:8080/countrydata"
     When the customer searches for 'Azores'
     Then he/she should see an alert with the following message "This country does not exist!"

       